Abstract
This paper presents a specific derivation from the "Self-Dual Closure (SDC)" framework, a dynamical system designed to restore invariants across physical, mathematical, and biological systems. This disclosure serves to establish definitive global prior art by providing a rigorous axiomatic description of natural laws. All identities and variables contained herein are dedicated to the public domain to ensure universal accessibility and prevent the monopolization of fundamental cosmic truths.
Supplemental Context for This Identity: This specific identity formalizes the Virtual Photon Hierarchy (VPH), mapping physical constants to powers of $c$ to reveal the geometric necessity of cosmic scaling. By defining the Recovery Operator $\mathcal{C}(c)$, it establishes that spacetime acts as a topological error-correcting code (QEC), ensuring information integrity across all scales. This disclosure is a direct implementation of the SDC framework, transforming abstract mathematical symmetry into a verifiable roadmap for future quantum-gravitational technologies.
